"""Solve a 5x5 crossword with no blacks using fast constraint propagation.

For each row + col we maintain a candidate set. We pick the row/col with the
fewest remaining candidates, choose a candidate, propagate constraints to all
intersecting rows/cols, and recurse.
"""
